QuietWhileHome.Description: Your dishwasher will automatically go into Quiet Mode when Nest™ knows you’re home.
QuietWhileHome.Name: Quiet While Home

WashWhileAway.name: Wash While Away
WashWhileAway.description: When Nest™ detects you're away, your dishwasher will start the selected cycle.  Please note that it may take up to two hours for Nest™ to send the away signal.

SmartEnergy.Description: Use Smart Delay to delay your dishwasher from running during peak energy hours.
SmartEnergy.Name: Smart Delay
